videos.description: Michigan center Hunter Dickinson finishes the and-1 over Brad Davison and lets the crowd know about it.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dickinson gives an and-1 celebration after finishing over Davison) 2022/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dickinson gives an and-1 celebration after finishing over Davison

videos.description: Johnny Davis blows by his defender and flips in the tough and-1 with his left hand.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnny Davis attacks basket for impressive and-1) 2022/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnny Davis attacks basket for impressive and-1

videos.description: Johnny Davis hits the tough fadeaway in the lane followed by a Brad Davison 3-pointer, putting the Badgers up 15 late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wisconsin puts Michigan away with Davis' fadeaway and Davison's 3) 2022/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin puts Michigan away with Davis' fadeaway and Davison's 3

videos.description: Michigan coach Juwan Howard strikes Wisconsin assistant coach Joe Krabbenhoft in the handshake line after game between Badgers and Wolverines.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Misc. (Juwan Howard throws blow at Wisconsin assistant after loss) 2022/02/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Juwan Howard throws blow at Wisconsin assistant after loss

videos.description: Juwan Howard and Greg Gard explain their sides of the story on what led to the scuffle during the handshake line.
